Introduction

Karin is the lead vocalist, lead rapper, and youngest member of the girl group ALICE (formerly ELRIS) under IOK Company. Karin is also known for being a contestant in the 6th season of the show "Kpop Star."

On May 3, 2024, Karin announced through Bubble that she would be leaving ALICE.
